text: Kiersey Nicole Clemons (born December 17, 1993) is an American actress and singer. She is known for her roles in Neighbors 2: Sorority Rising, Flatliners, Hearts Beat Loud, and the 2019 remake of Lady and the Tramp. She voiced the role of Dee Dee Skyes in the animated movie Scoob!. Clemons was cast as Iris West in the Justice League, but her scenes were cut and later restored in the 2021 director's cut. She played the role again in the 2023 movie The Flash. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:LGBT actors Category:LGBT singers Category:Actors from Florida Category:Singers from Florida Category:People from Pensacola, Florida
